org.eclipse.jst.jsf.common.metadata
Interface MetadataPackage

public interface MetadataPackage

The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type

NOT API

See Also:
MetadataFactory
